claim: Ecuador literally translates to "Republic of the Equator."
premise_source_doc_sentence: Ecuador  (  -LSB- ˈɛkwədɔːr -RSB- , -LSB- ekwaˈðor -RSB-  )   (  Ikwadur  )  , officially the Republic of Ecuador  (  -LSB- República del Ecuador , -RSB- , which literally translates as `` Republic of the Equator '' ; Ikwadur Ripuwlika  )  , is a representative democratic republic in northwestern South America , bordered by Colombia on the north , Peru on the east and south , and the Pacific Ocean to the west .
